---
title: Honey-Soy Chicken Tacos with Pear Slaw & Spring Onion
description: You think you know tacos? Think again: our Asian chicken filling changes the whole profile of these tacos with its honey-soy glaze.We love to top it with fresh carrot and pear and zingy spring onion for maximum deliciousness of this fusion cuisine.

*We’ve replaced the crispy shallots in this recipe with spring onion due to local ingredient availability. It’ll be just
as delicious, just follow your recipe card!*
